<?php foreach($model["rows"] as $key => $row) { ?> <?php if($row["isSuperUser"] && User::current()["id"] != $row["id"]) { continue; } ?><tr><td>#<?php echo $row["id"]; ?></td><td> <?php if($row["isSystem"]) { ?><span  class="material-symbols-outlined"  title="<?php echo t('System account'); ?>">smart_toy</span>  <?php } else if($row["isNotActive"]) { ?><span  class="material-symbols-outlined"  title="<?php echo t('The account has not been activated'); ?>">warning</span>  <?php } else if($row["isNotActiveAndBlocked"]) { ?><span  class="material-symbols-outlined"  title="<?php echo t('The account is inactive and blocked'); ?>">error</span>  <?php } else if($row["isBlocked"]) { ?><span  class="material-symbols-outlined"  title="<?php echo t('Blocked'); ?>">block</span>  <?php } else if($row["isSuperUser"]) { ?><span  class="material-symbols-outlined"  title="<?php echo t('Superuser'); ?>">badge</span>  <?php } ?></td><td> <?php echo $row["name"]; ?></td><td><a  href="mailto:<?php echo $row['email']; ?>"><?php echo $row["email"]; ?></a> </td><td> <?php if($row["isSystem"]) { ?><span  style="color:silver;"  class="system-account"><?php echo t("System account"); ?></span>  <?php } else { ?><span  style="color:<?php echo $row['permission']['color']; ?>;"><?php echo $row["permission"]["name"]; ?></span>  <?php } ?></td><td> <?php echo $row["ip"]; ?></td><td><a  href="<?php echo Router::url(); ?>adminv3/users/edit/<?php echo $row['id']; ?>"  class="button"><span  class="material-symbols-outlined">edit</span>   <?php echo t("Edit"); ?></a>   <?php if($row["isSuperUser"]) { ?><a  href="#"  class="button disabled"  disabled="disabled"  onclick="return false;"><span  class="material-symbols-outlined"  title="<?php echo t('Account cannot be deleted'); ?>">lock</span> </a>  <?php } else { ?><a  href="#"  class="button"  onclick="deleteUser('<?php echo $row["id"]; ?>');return false;"><span  class="material-symbols-outlined"  title="<?php echo t('Delete user'); ?>">delete</span> </a>  <?php } ?></td></tr> <?php } ?><script> var total_rows = <?php echo $model['total']; ?>;
    var page = <?php echo $model['page']; ?>;
    table_users.pushInfo({total: total_rows, page: page });
</script>